    "It has been in use in nursing facilities in Japan since 2003.",
    "It responds to tactile stimuli and recognizes temperature, posture, and light.",
    "9 Leiya Arata is a founder of the Love Doll Funeral services in Osaka.",
    "For $800 customers can have a mannequin memorial.",
    "Presiding over the mannequin memorials is the Buddhist monk Lay Kato."
